    bottom digivolution cards. Then, delete any number of your opponent's Digimon
    whose levels that add up to 4 or less. For every 2 [Argomon] in this Digimon's
    digivolution cards, add 1 to the maximum level you can choose with this effect.\n[All
    Turns] This Digimon gets +1000 DP for every 2 [Argomon] in its digivolution cards.\n[Opponent's
    Turn] None of your opponent's Tamers can unsuspend."
